	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>

	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><b>Our Provider Sanction Search contains nationwide coverage across multiple licensing entities covering Physicians, Chiropractors, Physical Therapists, Podiatrists, among others.</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><b>Quick Start:</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p>First, try to find a Provider Sanction record using the following search technique:</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<ol id="font81">
	  <li>Search by Individual or Company Name and State. If search is too broad, or too many records are returned, try adding a City. You can also use a partial first name. If both Individual name and Company name are input, only the Company name will be searched.<br /><br /></li>
	  <li>Search by Name (or Company Name), License Number & State.<br /><br /></li>
	  <li>Search by Name and DOB (MM/DD/YYYY).<br /><br /></li>
	  <li>Search by Name (or Company Name), Address, City, and State.<br /><br /></li>
	  <li>Search by Name (or Company Name), Tax ID (SSN or FEIN).<br /><br /></li>
	</ol>
